8:35.000Z","msg":"櫻桃的滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得錫蘭都好勁，winter sleep好有塔氏feel<br />\n但始終Kubrick 真係全能到仆街"},{"pid":"0a599ab266d0f1aea8dc2b6ecab7c803b759a88c","tid":2106354,"uid":7332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e3d65e4616de8823e9c5df05f6b8d7b49506f0f","tid":2106354,"uid":18430,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:06:31.000Z","msg":"當連史高西斯帶頭 de niro joe peci al Pacino 開戲都無電影公司投資得掂，最後得netflix 肯接，或者可以睇得出啲端倪<br />\n只可以講對於觀眾係可惜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T05:51:07.000Z","msg":"巴打應該對戲有好多睇法<br />\n遠至Fellini 拎完奧斯卡，有本寫佢既《夢是唯一的真實》，都有講到電視對電影既重大影響<br />\n依家更加走到極端，全球睇Netflix , 即食文化影響觀眾，之後art house movie 既去向真係一個迷"},{"pid":"64ec89d6689b0a53855c7770310df9033bc79678","tid":2106354,"uid":7332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"809eab1400b3b65850a217454f8944ea3fd9ccf4","tid":2106354,"uid":2737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T18:31:31.000Z","msg":"Kubrick 其實幾雅俗共賞我覺得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"最近睇完2001<br />\n覺得佢真係神，佢拍既每一套電影係可以成為𠴱個genre 既指標。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Kubrick 係追求完美同極限，追求電影呢種表現方法既極限，好似貝多芬咁。但好似塔可，就係追求內省同感覺，好似舒伯特"},{"pid":"5d2a975178f84a7905fbc6f54edbf509c62bedb7","tid":2106354,"uid":127039,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"Nolan 都唔算？我敢講佢嘅作品同Kubrick一樣咁劃時代"},{"pid":"533dd0d3327630da2845f9f1ba221de8717b74bd","tid":2106354,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"占士金馬倫"},{"pid":"eda47d60f899862167bc84e65eac6f0d482c3f11","tid":2106354,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"533dd0d3327630da2845f9f1ba221de8717b74bd","tid":2106354,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"占士金馬倫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDXPyZ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i