":{"pid":"533dd0d3327630da2845f9f1ba221de8717b74bd","tid":2106354,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"占士金馬倫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:21:29.000Z","msg":"不如ridley scott"},{"pid":"6dd5c3c6a7b80cad7a782d15686febbc5f10f954","tid":2106354,"uid":153570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:22:18.000Z","msg":"唔會再有了<br />\n我覺得世界所有野都倒退緊<br />\n人類文明最顛峰就係戰後果幾十年"},{"pid":"933a85a64ba6ef09f40ee4cd62c9444a844f8857","tid":2106354,"uid":7332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6dd5c3c6a7b80cad7a782d15686febbc5f10f954","tid":2106354,"uid":153570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:22:18.000Z","msg":"唔會再有了<br />\n我覺得世界所有野都倒退緊<br />\n人類文明最顛峰就係戰後果幾十年"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"真，究竟係咩攪到咁<br />\n<br />\nPainting成行俾gallery 同拍賣行攪亂檔，唔會再有van gogh <br />\n<br />\n音樂方面曾經有cage, ligeti 等人挑戰聲音既極限，超越左廿一世紀所有音樂家<br />\n<br />\n電影。好似無人再試啲好新既野。對上一次新野已經係Goodbye to Language, 但都係高達拍的。科技愈新，電影愈為娛樂而服務<br />\n<br />\n可能真係要黎多次世界大戰，哈哈"},{"pid":"41f0d1c9779372ddd8fe05288cb19bc03f358d6b","tid":2106354,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5dfeca1424357e3bbc13618d06e03d5b401474c","tid":2106354,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6fa77b7e08d338dde40cbfb915b2369c9e81008a","tid":2106354,"uid":157092,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢一代導演唯一接近啲嘅係Paul Thomas Anderson?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"There will be blood之後回塘回得好勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中意The Master 多啲"},{"pid":"413650383a3f5e16932882b662bf132591c9f9c2","tid":2106354,"uid":153570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"933a85a64ba6ef09f40ee4cd62c9444a844f8857","tid":2106354,"uid":7332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6dd5c3c6a7b80cad7a782d15686febbc5f10f954","tid":2106354,"uid":153570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:22:18.000Z","msg":"唔會再有了<br />\n我覺得世界所有野都倒退緊<br />\n人類文明最顛峰就係戰後果幾十年"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"真，究竟係咩攪到咁<br />\n<br />\nPainting成行俾gallery 同拍賣行攪亂檔，唔會再有van gogh <br />\n<br />\n音樂方面曾經有cage, ligeti 等人挑戰聲音既極限，超越左廿一世紀所有音樂家<br />\n<br />\n電影。好似無人再試啲好新既野。對上一次新野已經係Goodbye to Language, 但都係高達拍的。科技愈新，電影愈為娛樂而服務<br />\n<br />\n可能真係要黎多次世界大戰，哈哈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:47:17.000Z","msg":"人類就係咁, 和平得太耐就屎忽痕<br />\n但係呢個世界應該無quota再黎多次大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係我誇張, 呢個世界肉眼可見咁滅亡緊"},{"pid":"1a4f04488f1d35a235a7bae630fd6f2cf9aebb23","tid":2106354,"uid":262970,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T18:20:34.000Z","msg":"其實廿一世紀都係得20年<br />\n係kubrick之後 都仲有幾代嘅<br />\n雖然電影就好主觀嘅 但你話商業娛樂片係咪就一定好過cult片 就未必 <br />\n<br />\n求其up三個啦<br />\n<br />\n韓國李滄東 日本今敏 芬蘭Kaurism&auml;ki<br />\n三個都有自己一套特色，都係某一方面做得好極致。一直很模仿，從未被超越，有少少呢種感覺。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係以前電影未有好似而家咁普及，從業人員唔多，好多發展空間，會好自然造神。<br />\n<br />\n你而家睇新浪潮都感受唔到其實有幾革命性，但係當時好屈。如果往後嘅人越來越難突破個框框，咁其實做到少少突破已經好好。"},{"pid":"ee88a14d441fd86164b8c2512c0b1daf49601f1b","tid":2106354,"uid":300687,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:09:50.000Z","msg":"用「下一個 kubrick」呢個角度去睇係永遠都唔會有下一個 kubrick 或者 bergman<br />\n但廿一世紀有啲我覺得已經接近神台級：奉俊昊、阿彼察邦、賈樟柯、杜sir、是枝裕和<br />\n成熟穩重期：nolan、villeneuve、cuaron、wes anderson、asghar farhadi、audiard、dardenne brothers、kelly reichardt（呢批大把）<br />\n新一代都好有希望：<br />\nbarry jenkins、celine sciamma、greta gerwig、mati diop、jordan peele、steve mcqueen"},{"pid":"70e7e50e72e0eab535b592add7b30407c3f5b098","tid":2106354,"uid":300687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a5dfeca1424357e3bbc13618d06e03d5b401474c","tid":2106354,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6fa77b7e08d338dde40cbfb915b2369c9e81008a","tid":2106354,"uid":157092,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢一代導演唯一接近啲嘅係Paul Thomas Anderson?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"There will be blood之後回塘回得好勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:11:07.000Z","msg":"phantom thread 我覺得係出道至今最好"},{"pid":"25d2d1eca9d6d7eb15872ff191ab14ad4d00b2fd","tid":2106354,"uid":300687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"933a85a64ba6ef09f40ee4cd62c9444a844f8857","tid":2106354,"uid":7332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6dd5c3c6a7b80cad7a782d15686febbc5f10f954","tid":2106354,"uid":153570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:22:18.000Z","msg":"唔會再有了<br />\n我覺得世界所有野都倒退緊<br />\n人類文明最顛峰就係戰後果幾十年"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"真，究竟係咩攪到咁<br />\n<br />\nPainting成行俾gallery 同拍賣行攪亂檔，唔會再有van gogh <br />\n<br />\n音樂方面曾經有cage, ligeti 等人挑戰聲音既極限，超越左廿一世紀所有音樂家<br />\n<br />\n電影。好似無人再試啲好新既野。對上一次新野已經係Goodbye to Language, 但都係高達拍的。科技愈新，電影愈為娛樂而服務<br />\n<br />\n可能真係要黎多次世界大戰，哈哈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T19:14:50.000Z","msg":"唔覺得音樂冇，可能冇 john cage 咁出名，但仍然有好多人玩緊好有趣嘅嘢挑戰聲音極限，例如 caroline shaw、ted hearne、bang on a can 三位、andrew norman、john luther adams"}]}